data.description: Even with the higher interest rates, it's still cheaper to buy then rent! Take a look at this cute little home featuring 2 bedrooms with a main floor bedroom, laundry and 1-bathroom on the main floor as well, roomy kitchen with plenty of counter space, new flooring throughout the home and fresh paint. It also has a nice level backyard with a shed. Do not wait too long to look at this one because it will not last long!
